\c 15
\s Ukubusa kukaAbhiyamu
\p
\v 1 Ngomnyaka wetshumi lesificaminwembili wenkosi uJerobhowamu indodana kaNebati uAbhiyamu wasesiba yinkosi phezu kukaJuda\x + 2 Lan. 13.1,2.\x*.
\v 2 Wabusa iminyaka emithathu eJerusalema. Lebizo likanina lalinguMahaka indodakazi kaAbishalomu\x + 2 Lan. 11.20-22.\x*.
\v 3 Wasehamba ezonweni zonke zikayise ayezenze phambi kwakhe, lenhliziyo yakhe yayingaphelelanga kuJehova uNkulunkulu wakhe, njengenhliziyo kaDavida uyise\x + 8.61. 15.14. 2 Lan. 13.10.\x*.
\v 4 Kodwa ngenxa kaDavida iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakhe yamnika isibane eJerusalema, ngokubeka indodana yakhe emva kwakhe, langokuqinisa iJerusalema.
\v 5 Ngoba uDavida wenza okulungileyo emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd*, kaphambukanga kukho konke eyamlaya khona insuku zonke zempilo yakhe\x + 14.8. 9.4.\x*, ngaphandle kwedabeni lukaUriya umHethi\x + 2 Sam. 11.4,15; 12.9.\x*.
\v 6 Kwakukhona-ke impi phakathi kukaRehobhowamu loJerobhowamu zonke izinsuku zempilo yakhe\x + 14.30.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Ezinye-ke zezindaba zikaAbhiyamu, lakho konke akwenzayo, kakubhalwanga yini egwalweni lwemilando yamakhosi akoJuda\x + 2 Lan. 13.22.\x*? Njalo kwaba lempi phakathi kukaAbhiyamu loJerobhowamu\x + 2 Lan. 13.2.\x*.
\v 8 UAbhiyamu waselala laboyise, bamngcwabela emzini kaDavida. UAsa indodana yakhe wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe\x + 2 Lan. 14.1.\x*.
\s Ukubusa kukaAsa
\p
\v 9 Ngomnyaka wamatshumi amabili kaJerobhowamu inkosi yakoIsrayeli uAsa wasesiba yinkosi yakoJuda.
\v 10 Wasebusa iminyaka engamatshumi amane lanye eJerusalema. Lebizo likanina lalinguMahaka indodakazi kaAbishalomu.
\v 11 UAsa wasesenza okulungileyo emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd* njengoDavida uyise\x + 2 Lan. 14.2.\x*.
\v 12 Wasusa izinkotshana elizweni\x + Dute. 23.17.\x*, wasusa zonke izithombe oyise ababezenzile\x + Dute. 29.17. 2 Lan. 15.8.\x*.
\v 13 Laye-ke uMahaka unina\x + 2 Lan. 15.16-18.\x* wamsusa ekubeni yindlovukazi\x + 11.19.\x*, ngoba wayenze into enengekayo ibe yiAshera; uAsa waseyigamula into yakhe enengekayo, wayitshisela esifuleni\x + Eks. 32.20.\x* iKidroni\x + 2 Sam. 15.23.\x*.
\v 14 Kanti indawo eziphakemeyo kazisuswanga\x + 22.43. 2 Kho. 12.3; 14.4. 2 Lan. 15.17. 2 Kho. 18.4. 2 Lan. 14.3,5.\x*; lanxa kunjalo inhliziyo kaAsa yayiphelele kuJehova insuku zakhe zonke.
\v 15 Wasengenisa izinto ezehlukanisiweyo zikayise kanye lezakhe izinto ezehlukanisiweyo endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*, isiliva legolide lezitsha.
\s Isivumelwano sikaAsa loBenihadadi
\p
\v 16 Kwakukhona-ke impi phakathi kukaAsa loBahasha inkosi yakoIsrayeli zonke izinsuku zabo.
\v 17 UBahasha inkosi yakoIsrayeli wasesenyuka wamelana loJuda\x + 2 Lan. 16.1-6.\x*, wakha iRama\x + 15.21,22. Josh. 18.25.\x*, ukuze angavumeli muntu ukuphuma lokungena kuAsa inkosi yakoJuda\x + 12.27. 2 Lan. 11.16; 15.9.\x*.
\v 18 UAsa wasethatha sonke isiliva legolide okwakusele emagugwini endlu kaJehova lamagugu endlu yenkosi, wakunikela esandleni senceku zakhe\x + 14.26. 2 Kho. 12.18.\x*; inkosi uAsa yakuthumela kuBenihadadi indodana kaTabirimoni indodana kaHeziyoni, inkosi yeSiriya\x + 2 Lan. 16.7-9.\x*, owayehlala eDamaseko\x + 11.24.\x*, esithi:
\v 19 Kulesivumelwano phakathi kwami lawe, phakathi kukababa loyihlo; khangela, ngikuthumezela isipho, isiliva legolide\x + 2 Kho. 16.8.\x*. Hamba, yephula isivumelwano sakho loBahasha inkosi yakoIsrayeli, ukuze enyuke asuke kimi.
\v 20 UBenihadadi waseyilalela inkosi uAsa, wathuma induna zamabutho ayelawo emelene lemizi yakoIsrayeli, watshaya iIjoni\x + 2 Kho. 15.29.\x* leDani\x + Hlu. 18.29.\x* leAbeli-Beti-Mahaka\x + 2 Sam. 20.14. 2 Kho. 15.29. Hlu. 11.33. 2 Lan. 16.4.\x* layo yonke iKinerothi lelizwe lonke lakoNafithali\x + Josh. 11.2.\x*.
\v 21 Kwasekusithi uBahasha e\add ku\add*zwa wayekela ukwakha iRama\x + 15.21,22. Josh. 18.25.\x*, wahlala eTiriza\x + 14.17.\x*.
\v 22 Inkosi uAsa yasisenza isimemezelo kuyo yonke iJuda; kakho owayetshiywe ngaphandle; ukuze basuse amatshe eRama lezigodo zayo, uBahasha ayesakha ngakho. Inkosi uAsa wasesakha ngakho iGeba yakoBhenjamini\x + Josh. 18.24.\x* leMizipa\x + Jer. 41.6,9,10. Josh. 18.26.\x*.
\p
\v 23 Ezinye-ke zazo zonke indaba zikaAsa, lawo wonke amandla akhe, lakho konke akwenzayo, lemizi ayakhayo, kakubhalwanga yini egwalweni lwemilando yamakhosi akoJuda\x + 2 Lan. 16.11.\x*? Kodwa esikhathini sobudala bakhe wayelomkhuhlane ezinyaweni\x + 2 Lan. 16.12.\x*.
\v 24 UAsa waselala laboyise, wangcwatshelwa kuboyise emzini kaDavida uyise. UJehoshafathi indodana yakhe wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe\x + 2 Lan. 16.13. 17. 1.\x*.
\s Ukubusa kukaNadabi
\p
\v 25 UNadabi indodana kaJerobhowamu wasesiba yinkosi phezu kukaIsrayeli ngomnyaka wesibili kaAsa inkosi yakoJuda\x + 14.20.\x*; wabusa phezu kukaIsrayeli iminyaka emibili.
\v 26 Wasesenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd*, wahamba ngendlela kayise, lesonweni sakhe, enza uIsrayeli one ngaso\x + 14.16.\x*.
\p
\v 27 UBahasha indodana kaAhiya, owendlu kaIsakari, wasemenzela ugobe\x + 14.14.\x*; uBahasha wamtshaya eGibethoni engeyamaFilisti\x + 16.15. Josh. 19.44.\x*, lapho uNadabi loIsrayeli wonke bevimbezele iGibethoni.
\v 28 UBahasha wambulala-ke ngomnyaka wesithathu kaAsa inkosi yakoJuda, wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe.
\v 29 Kwasekusithi ekubuseni kwakhe watshaya yonke indlu kaJerobhowamu, katshiyanga loyedwa ophefumulayo kuJerobhowamu, waze wamqeda, njengelizwi leN\nd kosi\x + 14.10,14.\x*\nd* eyalikhuluma ngesandla senceku yayo uAhiya umShilo\x + 11.29.\x*.
\v 30 Ngenxa yezono zikaJerobhowamu azonayo, lowenza uIsrayeli azone, ngentukuthelo yakhe athukuthelisa ngayo iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli\x + 14.9,16.\x*.
\p
\v 31 Ezinye-ke zezindaba zikaNadabi, lakho konke akwenzayo, kakubhalwanga yini egwalweni lwemilando yamakhosi akoIsrayeli?
\s Ukubusa kukaBahasha
\p
\v 32 Njalo kwakulempi phakathi kukaAsa loBahasha inkosi yakoIsrayeli insuku zabo zonke\x + 15.16. 2 Lan. 16.9.\x*.
\v 33 Ngomnyaka wesithathu kaAsa inkosi yakoJuda uBahasha indodana kaAhiya waba yinkosi phezu kukaIsrayeli wonke eTiriza\x + 15.34.\x*; iminyaka engamatshumi amabili lane.
\v 34 Wasesenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd*, wahamba ngendlela kaJerobhowamu, lesonweni sakhe, enza uIsrayeli one ngaso\x + 15.26. 12.28,29; 13.33; 14.16; 16.2,13,19,26.\x*.
